'''巧控滑鼠'''（Magic Mouse）是由[[蘋果公司|蘋果公司]]出品和發售的[[多點觸控|多點觸控]]（Multi-touch）[[滑鼠|滑鼠]]<ref name = "Magic Mouse" >{{cite web
    | url = http://www.apple.com/magicmouse/
    | title = 巧控滑鼠
    | publisher = Apple
    | accessdate = {{start date|2009|12|01}}
    | archive-date = 2015-10-06
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151006170405/http://www.apple.com/magicmouse/
    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref>，它在2009年10月20日宣佈和發售<ref name = "Engadget-announcement" >{{cite web
    | url = http://www.engadget.com/2009/10/20/apples-magic-mouse-multitouch-gestures-bluetooth-four-month/
    | title = Apple's Magic Mouse: one button, multitouch gestures, Bluetooth, four-month battery life
    | last = Topolsky
    | first = Joshua
    | date = {{start date|2009|10|20}}
    | publisher = Engadget
    | accessdate = {{start date|2009|10|25}}
    | archive-date = 2019-07-20
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190720185910/http://www.engadget.com/2009/10/20/apples-magic-mouse-multitouch-gestures-bluetooth-four-month/
    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref>。巧控滑鼠是世界上首個引入多點觸控技術的滑鼠<ref name = "Magic Mouse" />。繼[[iPhone|iPhone]]、[[iPad|iPad]]、[[iPod_Touch|iPod Touch]]和觸控板後，巧控滑鼠容許用户使用不同的[[手勢識別|手勢]]，例如在滑鼠表面上輕掃和滾動，便可達到特定的效果。巧控滑鼠經[[藍牙|藍牙]]技術連接，而且以內置電池驱動。

巧控滑鼠與[[Mac_OS_X_v10.5|Mac OS X 10.5.8]]及更新系统相容。它可以被設定為雙鍵、適合左撇子或右撇子的滑鼠，儘管它的預設設定是單鍵滑鼠。它使用[[鼠标#技術|鐳射追踪]]，比早期蘋果滑鼠更有準確性<ref name = "Apple store" >{{cite web
    | url = http://store.apple.com/us/product/MB829LL/A
    | title = Magic Mouse
    | publisher = Apple
    | accessdate = {{start date|2009|10|25}}
    | archive-date = 2012-05-23
    | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120523155446/http://store.apple.com/us/product/MB829LL/A
    | dead-url = no
    }}</ref>。自它發行以來，它已經與蘋果無線鍵盤一起包括在2009年的[[iMac|iMac]]和與蘋果有線鍵盤一起包括在2010年的[[Mac_Pro|Mac Pro]]工作台中。而Magic Mouse也能單獨購買。

